title: Joseline Hernandez Interview,  Regina Hall Interview and More
itunes:title: Joseline Hernandez Interview,  Regina Hall Interview and More
description:
Friday 7/21- Today on the show we had the "Puerto Rican Princess" Joseline Hernandez from Love and Hip Hop visit and she let us in on mother hood, quitting LAHH and even her ta-tas, literally! Also we had Regina Hall stop by to promote the movie "Girls Trip". Charlamagne also gave "Donkey of the Day" to a man who is running for mayor in Florida and told black activist to go back to Africa.
